<div class="article-body" id="Body"><p class="no-indent">Set the scene for a Halloween party in a wide-open outdoor space. Kick it off by lighting a bonfire. A buffet table with all the fixings will attract guests to build their ultimate hot dog. As sweet cravings strike, they can revisit the buffet to collect the makings for the perfect party finish—melty chocolate s’mores.</p><br/><p>______________________________</p><br/><p class="no-indent">Southern-style Barbecue Dog </p><p class="no-indent">Coleslaw, dill pickle spear, and barbecue sauce </p><br/><p class="no-indent">Delicatessen Dog </p><p class="no-indent">Sauerkraut, spicy mustard, and chopped red onion </p><br/><p class="no-indent">Cowboy Dog </p><p class="no-indent">Peppery Chili, shredded cheese, and sliced red onion</p><br/><p class="no-indent">Haute Dog </p><p class="no-indent">Caramelized Onions, Mushrooms, and Bacon with crumbled blue cheese </p><br/><p class="no-indent">Nacho Ordinary Dog </p><p class="no-indent">Hot Nacho Cheese Dip, sliced pickled jalapeños, diced tomatoes, and sliced black olives</p></div>
